Alembic migrations for Vibedeck.

The database URL comes from .env (DATABASE_URL) via migrations/env.py,
not from alembic.ini. Models are imported from backend/models.

Common commands (run from the repo root):

    alembic revision --autogenerate -m "create initial schema"
    alembic upgrade head
    alembic downgrade -1
    alembic history

No migration has been generated yet — the initial schema is pending
review of backend/models before the first autogenerate.
